List all available options for Kodi:confopts_ph.sh -p list -a Kodi | more
View the value of any Kodi option(s) (Variable expansion disabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Kodi -g
View the value of any Kodi option(s) (Variable expansion enabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Kodi -g -r
View/Change the value of read-write Kodi option(s) (Variable expansion disabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Kodi -s
View/Change the value of read-write Kodi option(s) (Variable expansion enabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Kodi -s -r
Set all Kodi options back to default:ph_set_all_options_to_default Kodi
Display help for Kodi option(s) (Variable expansion disabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Kodi -d
Display help for Kodi option(s) (Variable expansion enabled):confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Kodi -d -r
Go to Main menu:ph_show_menu Main
Go to Apps menu:ph_show_menu Apps
Open Shell to home directory (Type 'CTRL-D' to return):cd;/bin/bash
Return to previous screen:return
